## Details about Problem
A package information in the   looks like 
```json
"centralTransitiveDependencyGroups": {
    ".NETFramework,Version=v4.7.2": {
      "EnvDTE": {
        "include": "Runtime, Compile, Native, BuildTransitive",
        "target": "Package",
        "version": "[8.0.2, )",
        "versionCentrallyManaged": true
      },
```
The issue is about removing target and versionCentrallyManaged elements to be transformed to

```json
"centralTransitiveDependencyGroups": {
    ".NETFramework,Version=v4.7.2": {
      "EnvDTE": {
        "include": "Runtime, Compile, Native, BuildTransitive",
        "version": "[8.0.2, )"
      },
```
